PrecisOrder fixing (a) MONDAY, SEPTEMBER 1, 1997, as the day upon which a number of provisions of this Act, being chapter 24 of the Statutes of Canada, 1997 [BILL C-32], shall COME INTO FORCE, and (b) THURSDAY, JANUARY 1, 1998, as the day upon which section 67 and subsections 67.1(1) and (2) of the Copyright Act [as enacted by section 45] shall COME INTO FORCE.
